title: How Quitting Can Make You a Winner
itunes:title: How Quitting Can Make You a Winner
description:
Annie Duke, former professional poker player and Partner at First Round Capital, discusses her book Quit: The Power of Knowing When to Walk Away.
Hosts: Carol Massar and Ed Ludlow. Producer: Paul Brennan.
